以下罰金：\r\n二、毀越門窗、牆垣或其他安全設備而犯之。\r\n三、攜帶兇器而犯之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/HLDM/110%2c%e6%98%93%2c305%2c20220210%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"HLDM,110,易,305,20220210,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"易","JNO":"305","JDATE":"20220210","JTITLE":"竊盜"}